# Usage
<!-- usage -->
```sh-session
$ npm install -g @oclif/plugin-which
$ oclif-example COMMAND
running command...
$ oclif-example (--version)
@oclif/plugin-which/2.1.0 linux-x64 node-v12.22.9
$ oclif-example --help [COMMAND]
USAGE
  $ oclif-example COMMAND
...
```

# Commands
<!-- commands -->
* [`oclif-example which`](#oclif-example-which)

## `oclif-example which`

Show which plugin a command is in.

```
USAGE
  $ oclif-example which

DESCRIPTION
  Show which plugin a command is in.
```

_See code: [src/commands/which.ts](https://github.com/oclif/plugin-which/blob/v2.1.0/src/commands/which.ts)_
